	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You hold out a morsel of food appropriate for an animal in front of you. As you whisper, your words sooth the creature to convince it you mean no harm.</em></p><p><strong>Wisdom</strong> <strong>Save</strong> </p><p>The target &amp;reference[beast]{beast} must be able to see and hear you. If the beast's Intelligence is 4 or higher, the spell fails.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target is &amp;reference[charmed] by you and your allies, but is not compelled to do as you say.</p><p>If you or one of your allies harms the target, the spell ends.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> Target one additional beast for each spell level above 1st.</p>",
			"chat": "<p><strong>Wisdom</strong> <strong>Save</strong></p><p>The target &amp;reference[beast]{beast} must be able to see and hear you. If the beast's Intelligence is 4 or higher, the spell fails.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target is &amp;reference[charmed] by you and your allies, but is not compelled to do as you say.</p><p>If you or one of your allies harms the target, the spell ends.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> Target one additional beast for each spell level above 1st.</p>"
